OF STUPID.

04:14.030 --> 04:15.850
BUT, UM, I HAVE
TO GO TO SCHOOL.

04:15.860 --> 04:18.055
SO, I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

04:20.600 --> 04:22.693
( door closing )

04:23.760 --> 04:26.024
