YOU KNOW, I'LL PUT IT IN STORAGE
WITH THE REST OF MY STUFF.

05:01.960 --> 05:04.895
OH, SHIT, I GO'I'I'A RETURN
"A GREAT ESCAPE" TODAY.

05:04.900 --> 05:06.788
I'M GONNA
BE FUCKING LATE.

