IT'S ON MY WAY.

05:08.500 --> 05:11.151
I NEVER GET TIRED
OF WATCHING STEVE MCQUEEN.

05:11.160 --> 05:14.618
I THINK I'VE SEEN EVERY ONE OF
HIS MOVIES AT LEAST THREE TIMES.

05:14.630 --> 05:16.552
