A FORMALITY.

05:48.660 --> 05:50.457
CUT THE BULLSHIT
AND JUST SIGN IT.

05:50.460 --> 05:51.427
OKAY.

05:55.860 --> 05:58.021
YOU KNOW WHAT'S WEIRD
ABOUT DEAD PEOPLE ?

05:58.030 --> 05:59.497
