OF COURSE I WOULD'VE LOVED
TO DO THIS WITH SOMEONE

06:27.030 --> 06:29.055
WHO WANTED
TO BE A FATHER.

06:29.060 --> 06:30.721
I'M SORRY.

06:31.960 --> 06:34.019
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT ELSE TO--

06:34.030 --> 06:36.555
BUT THEN I THINK
HOW PERFECT THIS BABY IS.

06:36.560 --> 06:38.790
AND EVERYTHING
SOMEHOW SEEMS RIGHT.

06:42.030 --> 06:44.294
SOMEHOW
IT'S JUST SO FUNNY.

06:44.300 --> 06:47.394
AND YOU KNOW, ACTUALLY,
I'M PROUD IN A WEIRD WAY.

06:47.400 --> 06:49.220
